data.name: admin_task_list_description
data.value:
Description:
After configuring the farms Core Services, you can install Microsoft Office Project Web Access. First, you must specify the following information:
1) The Project Web Access site location: Select the host SharePoint Web application and then type the URL to Project Web Access.
2) The administrator account: Type the account information of the person who will be added as the first server administrator.
3) Primary database settings: Type the name of the server on which the primary Project Server databases will be created, and then type the names of those databases.
4) Secondary database settings: Type the name of the server on which the reporting database will be created, and then type the name of that database.
After you submit this information, Project Web Access can be accessed.
